So? Is that so? <br>
I don't agree Remfin.<br>
<br>
Please do't get me wrong Samadhi and Remfin. I am NOT a druid basher amd surerly, we are great at level 60. I know our power at level 60, especially on raids.<br>
<br>
My point is tho:<br>
<br>
As the ones that 'specialized' in nukage, there should be no other class come that close to us.<br>
As oftenly mentioned, when Sunstrike was released with Kunark some people were disappointed about the damage output.<br>
<br>
I am rather disapointed about the casteing time. Throwing instead of Sunstrike some Draughts of fire agains Mobs in a raid situation ususally gets me the kill. I don't think it should work like this.<br>
<br>
Well, as you agree, Druids are the MOST versatile class. They are now nukeing better even than Mages. Is that really a nessecary upgrade?<br>
<br>
Aren't there other spells out that would fir better into the Druids class description than an Ice Comet like nuke?<br>
<br>
Many WIzards are bceomming sensitive, i am one of them. Look, what Verant will give us, and look what Verant is giveing other classes.<br>
<br>
They said 'no you won't get any improved damage output, nulkes, mana regen etc...'<br>
But the give that all to other classes.<br>
<br>
Not only Druids, ALL other nukeing classes get upgraded nukes.<br>
<br>
I am a little 'pissed' about that 250 mana 750 POISON based shammy nuke as well.<br>
I don't think it will be resisted a lot, and again, another class rivals the Wizards in nukeing.<br>
<br>
I am NOT jealous, but every class should have their place in the game, in ecp groups in pickup groups etc.<br>
Our realm is the power of nukes. It should't be rivaled in any form, not in numbers on the paper, nor in game.<br>
<br>
Btw, for all of you, that said Mages bolts wouldn't hit a single target in raid situation...<br>
Try this:<br>
<br>
Head to ToV. <br>
Have 25 plus people bashing on the Mob.<br>
Mem your level 8 fire bolt spell.<br>
See how often it will hit it's target: ALLWAYS!<br>
<br>
And those bolts are powerfull, guys, REAL powerfull.<br>
<br>
So, if you come again to me about something with LoS and bolts - then i can only loaugh. They have NO problem to hit those Mobs.<br>
